title: 99. Call on Me (Ryan Riback Remix) - Starley
text: Absolutely in love with the lyrics and the beat. Biography Genre: Dance Starley is a dance-pop singer/songwriter from Sydney, New South Wales, Australia. A music lover since childhood, she moved to London to pursue a career in music, eventually working with a variety of producers and songwriters throughout the U.K., Sweden, and the United States. It wasn't until she moved back to Australia that her career began to take off. In 2016, she was the featured vocalist on Odd Mob's "Into You," which went to number one on the Australian club charts.
